data.text:
Welcome to Wemme ...

Wemme is located in Clackamas County<1>.

The location of Wemme has been provided by the Geographic Names Information System (ie- the GNIS).<2>

While we don't have a date for the founding of Wemme, you might consider that their post office opened in 1916.

Wemme is 1,320 feet [402 m] above sea level.<3>.

Time Zone: Wemme lies in the Pacific Time Zone (PST/PDT) and observes daylight saving time

Area codes for Wemme: (503) & (971)<4>

Using the information from an 1895 Atlas, we've created a list of communities that were in the area of Wemme. Our list includes information such as whether the 1895 community had a post office or railroad service. See our List of 1890's Communities around Wemme.

We also have a detailed list of newspapers that have been published in the area around Wemme. See our Newspapers Page for Wemme.

TripAdvisor Tourism Pages for Wemme ...

Looking for more information about Wemme? A wonderful source is the TripAdvisor website. We always start with the TripAdvisor Tourism page, where you can read an overview with links that will help you find lodging, restaurants and attractions.

While we are unaware of a Tourism page that is specific to Wemme, there are neighboring communities that do have Tourism pages. A map of those communities can be found with our TripAdvisor Page for Wemme.

Adding Wemme to Our Gazetteer ...

We originally found mention of Wemme in both the FIPS-55 and the GNIS. For more information, see the FIPS and GNIS Codes sections on our Miscellaneous Page.

From our notes, the earliest published mention we've found for Wemme was in the document titled List of Post Offices from Cameron Blevins and Richard Helbock.<6>

From that list, the Wemme post office opened in 1916.

For more details, see References and Mentions for Wemme.
